{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-449-chocolate-covered-candy","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-401-to-480","demoType":null,"title":"Zoezi la 449: Bomboni punjeni čokoladom","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Fil, proizvođač bombona, pravi novu seriju bombona sa punjenjem od čokolade. Svako jezgro bombona je kreirano kao cilindrični elipsoid definisan jednačinom: $b^2x^2 + b^2y^2 + a^2z^2 = a^2b^2$.</p>\n<p>Fil želi da sazna koliko čokolade je potrebno za pokrivanje jedne slatkišne srži, u ravnom sloju čokolade debljine jednog milimetra.</p>\n<p>Ako $a = 1$ mm i $b = 1$ mm, potrebna količina čokolade je $\\frac{28}{3} \\pi$ mm<sup>3</sup>.</p>\n<p>Ako su $a = 2$ mm i $b = 1$ mm, potrebna količina čokolade je približno 60.35475635 mm<sup>3</sup>.</p>\n<p>Pronađite količinu čokolade za mm<sup>3</sup> koja je potrebna ako $a = 3$ mm i $b = 1$ mm. Navedite svoj odgovor kao broj zaokružen na 8 decimalnih mesta iza decimalne tačke.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f52d1000cf542c510040","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":302121,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-449-chocolate-covered-candy"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function chocolateCoveredCandy() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\nchocolateCoveredCandy();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>chocolateCoveredCandy()</code> trebalo bi da vrati <code>103.37870096</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(chocolateCoveredCandy(), 103.37870096);"}]}}},"pageContext":{